msgctxt "887"
msgid ""
"龍馬が京の街を散策していると\n"
"何事かをもめている地主と神主\n"
"そして「遥」という名の少女と出会う"
msgstr ""
"As Ryoma strolls through the city of Kyoto, he meets a landowner, a priest, "
"and a girl named \"Haruka\" who are worried about something."

msgctxt "982"
msgid ""
"聞けば、遥の両親は借金を残したまま他界……\n"
"その借金を返済するため、いま住んでいる\n"
"家を売ることになったという話だった"
msgstr ""
"I heard that Haruka's parents passed away while leaving their debts ... To "
"repay their debts, they decided to sell the house they live in."

msgctxt "1101"
msgid ""
"少女・遥との縁を感じた龍馬は\n"
"詳しい事情を聞くため、彼女の生家へと向かった"
msgstr ""
"Ryoma, who felt a connection with the girl Haruka, headed to her birthplace "
"to hear more about the situation."

msgctxt "1176"
msgid ""
"すると、遥は両親の温もりと思い出が残る\n"
"この家から離れたくないと、涙ながらに\n"
"自らの思いを口にする"
msgstr ""
"Then, Haruka tearfully expresses her feelings that she does not want to "
"leave this house where her parents' warmth and memories remain."

msgctxt "1275"
msgid ""
"その話を聞いた龍馬は、彼女の借金を肩代わりし\n"
"その家を自分の別宅として使い\n"
"遥を住まわせるという決断をした……"
msgstr ""
"Upon hearing the story, Ryoma decided to take over her debt and use the "
"house as her own separate house to live in Haruka ..."
